<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Associative Law</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    background: #0d0d14;
    color: #e8e4d9;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    gap: 36px;
  }

  .page-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    color: #f5f0e8;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-sub {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #555;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .card {
    background: #13131e;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 30px;
    width: min(700px, 96vw);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both;
  }
  .card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; border: 1px solid #3b82f630; }
  .card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.2s; border: 1px solid #a855f730; }

  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px); }
    to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .add-card .card-title { color: #60a5fa; }
  .mul-card .card-title { color: #c084fc; }

  .badge {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .add-card .badge { background:#1d4ed830; color:#60a5fa; border:1px solid #3b82f640; }
  .mul-card .badge { background:#7e22ce30; color:#c084fc; border:1px solid #a855f740; }

  .formula {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(0.78rem, 2.2vw, 0.98rem);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .add-card .formula { background:#1e2a3a; border:1px solid #3b82f630; color:#93c5fd; }
  .mul-card .formula { background:#1e1a2e; border:1px solid #a855f730; color:#d8b4fe; }

  /* ── ADDITION visuals ── */
  .visual-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 18px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .eq-sign { font-size:1.5rem; color:#555; font-family:'Playfair Display',serif; }

  .group-wrap { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px; }
  .block-row  { display:flex; gap:4px; align-items:center; }

  .block {
    width:34px; height:34px; border-radius:6px;
    border:2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    transition: transform 0.18s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .block:hover { transform:scale(1.2); }
  .block.yellow { background:#f59e0b; border-color:#d97706; }
  .block.teal   { background:#14b8a6; border-color:#0d9488; }
  .block.pink   { background:#ec4899; border-color:#db2777; }

  /* bracket highlight */
  .bracket-box {
    border: 2px dashed;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 4px 6px;
    display:flex; gap:4px; align-items:center;
  }
  .bracket-box.blue  { border-color:#3b82f6; background:#1e3a5f22; }
  .bracket-box.green { border-color:#22c55e; background:#14532d22; }

  .plus { font-size:1.1rem; color:#666; margin:0 2px; }

  .group-label {
    font-size:0.62rem; color:#888;
    letter-spacing:0.06em; text-align:center;
  }

  .hint {
    font-size:0.6rem; color:#444; letter-spacing:0.12em;
    text-transform:uppercase; text-align:center;
  }

  /* ── 3-D CUBE (CSS only) ── */
  .cubes-row {
    display:flex; align-items:flex-end;
    justify-content:center; gap:40px; flex-wrap:wrap;
  }
  .cube-wrap { display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
  .cube-label { font-size:0.68rem; color:#aaa; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-align:center; }
  .cube-label span { font-weight:600; }
  .mul-card .cube-label .h { color:#f472b6; }
  .mul-card .cube-label .w { color:#60a5fa; }
  .mul-card .cube-label .l { color:#4ade80; }

  /* isometric cube made of 3 faces */
  .iso {
    position:relative;
    width:120px; height:104px;
    cursor:default;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .iso:hover { transform: scale(1.06); }

  .iso .face {
    position:absolute;
    display:grid;
    gap:2px;
  }

  /* Top face */
  .iso .top {
    width:80px; height:46px;
    top:0; left:20px;
    transform: skewX(-30deg) scaleY(0.6);
    transform-origin: bottom left;
  }
  /* Left face */
  .iso .left {
    width:40px; height:60px;
    bottom:0; left:0;
    transform: skewY(30deg);
    transform-origin: top right;
  }
  /* Right face */
  .iso .right {
    width:80px; height:60px;
    bottom:0; left:40px;
    transform: skewY(-15deg);
    transform-origin: top left;
  }

  .iso .cell {
    border-radius:2px;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    transition: opacity 0.15s;
  }
  .iso .cell:hover { opacity:0.7; }

  /* color themes for the two cubes */
  .cube-a .top  .cell { background:#a78bfa; }
  .cube-a .left .cell { background:#7c3aed; }
  .cube-a .right .cell { background:#c4b5fd; }

  .cube-b .top  .cell { background:#34d399; }
  .cube-b .left .cell { background:#059669; }
  .cube-b .right .cell { background:#6ee7b7; }

  /* ── Insight ── */
  .insight {
    width: min(700px, 96vw);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a10,#141410);
    border:1px solid #ca8a0440;
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:20px 28px;
    font-size:0.72rem;
    line-height:1.9;
    color:#d4b96a;
    animation: fadeUp 0.5s 0.3s ease both;
  }
  .insight strong { font-size:0.78rem; display:block; margin-bottom:6px;
    letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div>
  <h1 class="page-title">The Associative Law</h1>
  <p class="page-sub">To associate = to join each other</p>
</div>

<!-- ══ ADDITION ══ -->
<div class="card add-card">
  <div class="card-title">
    ➕ Associative Law of Addition
    <span class="badge">m+(n+k) = (m+n)+k</span>
  </div>

  <div class="formula">m + (n + k) = (m + n) + k &nbsp;&nbsp; for all m, n, k ∈ ℕ</div>

  <div class="visual-row">

    <!-- m + (n+k) -->
    <div class="group-wrap">
      <div class="block-row">
        <!-- m = 3 yellow -->
        <div class="block yellow"></div>
        <div class="block yellow"></div>
        <div class="block yellow"></div>
        <span class="plus">+</span>
        <!-- (n+k) = 2 teal + 2 pink -->
        <div class="bracket-box blue">
          <div class="block teal"></div>
          <div class="block teal"></div>
          <span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="block pink"></div>
          <div class="block pink"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="group-label">m + (n + k) &nbsp;=&nbsp; 3 + (2+2)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="eq-sign">=</div>

    <!-- (m+n) + k -->
    <div class="group-wrap">
      <div class="block-row">
        <!-- (m+n) = 3 yellow + 2 teal -->
        <div class="bracket-box green">
          <div class="block yellow"></div>
          <div class="block yellow"></div>
          <div class="block yellow"></div>
          <span class="plus">+</span>
          <div class="block teal"></div>
          <div class="block teal"></div>
        </div>
        <span class="plus">+</span>
        <!-- k = 2 pink -->
        <div class="block pink"></div>
        <div class="block pink"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="group-label">(m + n) + k &nbsp;=&nbsp; (3+2) + 2</div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="hint">↔ grouping changes — total stays the same: 7</div>
</div>


<!-- ══ MULTIPLICATION ══ -->
<div class="card mul-card">
  <div class="card-title">
    ✖️ Associative Law of Multiplication
    <span class="badge">m(nk) = (mn)k</span>
  </div>

  <div class="formula">m(nk) = (mn)k &nbsp;&nbsp; for all m, n, k ∈ ℕ</div>

  <div class="cubes-row">

    <!-- Cube A: height × (width × length) -->
    <div class="cube-wrap">
      <div class="cube-label">
        <span class="h">height</span> × (<span class="w">width</span> × <span class="l">length</span>)
      </div>

      <div class="iso cube-a">
        <!-- top: 4 cols × 3 rows -->
        <div class="face top" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,17px); grid-template-rows:repeat(3,13px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- left: 1 col × 4 rows -->
        <div class="face left" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(1,36px); grid-template-rows:repeat(4,14px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- right: 4 cols × 4 rows -->
        <div class="face right" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,18px); grid-template-rows:repeat(4,14px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cube-label">
        <span class="h">3</span> × (<span class="w">4</span> × <span class="l">4</span>) = 3×16 = 48
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="eq-sign" style="margin-bottom:30px">=</div>

    <!-- Cube B: (height × width) × length -->
    <div class="cube-wrap">
      <div class="cube-label">
        (<span class="h">height</span> × <span class="w">width</span>) × <span class="l">length</span>
      </div>

      <div class="iso cube-b">
        <div class="face top" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,17px); grid-template-rows:repeat(3,13px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="face left" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(1,36px); grid-template-rows:repeat(4,14px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="face right" style="grid-template-columns:repeat(4,18px); grid-template-rows:repeat(4,14px);">
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
          <div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div><div class="cell"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cube-label">
        (<span class="h">3</span> × <span class="w">4</span>) × <span class="l">4</span> = 12×4 = 48
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="hint">↔ grouping changes — volume stays the same: 48</div>
</div>

<!-- ── Insight ── -->
<div class="insight">
  <strong>💡 Key Insight</strong>
  The associative law says: it doesn't matter HOW you group the numbers, the result is always the same.
  For addition — changing which pair you add first doesn't change the total.
  For multiplication — a 3D box has the same volume whether you calculate height × (width × length) or (height × width) × length first.
  The brackets move, but the answer never changes.
</div>

</body>
</html>

